Package com.google.gdata.devtools.eclipse

Class Summary
Activator The activator class controls the plug-in life cycle
DependencyConfig A DependencyConfig object holds all the information pertaining to a particular external dependency.
DependencyConfigParser A utility class to parse the external dependency configuration file and return a collection of all the dependency configuration elements.
DependencyManager A utility class to provide various functionalities for the dependencies.
ExceptionHandler A utility class to provide exception handling.
FileTemplateConfig A FileTemplateConfig object holds all the information pertaining to a particular template.
FileTemplateConfigParser A utility class to parse the template configuration file and return a collection of all the template configuration elements.
ProjectCreator This class creates a Java Project in the workspace along with the referenced libraries required for a particular template.
